      <div class="msgContentFrame">The problem I find is that I can't AOE Heal spam without ripping Hate a lot of the times. So this forces me to single target heal - which drains my HP down. It's not horrible - but if someone is taking a bunch of damage up front and I have to stop to heal myself or switch on AoE with a macro - that sort of delay will kill someone. It also puts you low on health and if you eat an AoE or pull aggro you're that much more dead. <br /> <br />On my 13 THM I have Sacrifice and Cure equipped personally. I alternate them when constant healign is needed and keep the regen up otherwise.</div>
