      <div class="msgContentFrame">just get them both, i spam aoe sacrifice 2 as i need to no problem, normally my tank keeps the hate unless i messed up and pulled mobs w/o noticing with an aoe damage or if we get aggro i might end up with hate, but i have enough hp and good gear to resist that, all the healers i get into my parties die 1-2 hits from mobs, me and my tank dont like to worry much about having to protect other ppl so he rly does not have provoke set up, just the occasional taunt, and we dont have any problems. <br /> <br />ps: mostly we end up duoing since the ppl we invite either cant land hits before mob is dead or are healers that die by a bslap. <br /> <br />so just use cure 2 when your own hp is at stake since S2 does around 321(i have kept my mnd caped at 100 by choice) same as C2(thm both heals do equal healing) but S2 is minus 94 hp thats required for casting it. <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Oct 19th 2010  1:48am by AggroDoctor </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><a href="HTTP://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=4127062" rel="external nofollow" title="lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=4127062">Aggro Doctor's Rap Sheet</a> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1815324.png" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
